item.title: CVE-2023-22834|2024-08-02T10:20:30.681Z -- palantir -- com.palantir.contour%3Acontour-dispatch
item.description: The Contour Service was not checking that users had permission to create an analysis for a given dataset. This could allow an attacker to clutter up Compass folders with extraneous analyses, that the attacker would otherwise not have permission to create.
